==German==
===Etymology===
Compound of [[NHG]] ''[[klein]]'' ("small") + ''[[Buchstabe]]'' ("letter").  [[klein|Klein]] from [[OHG]] ''[[klein]]'' ("small", "sharp-witted", "fine"); [[Buchstabe]] from OHG ''[[buohstab]]'' ("letter", "writing"). 
